869
01:00:39,240 --> 01:00:40,800
 nismo baš najbolji.

870
01:00:40,800 --> 01:00:42,200
 Treba organizirati

871
01:00:42,200 --> 01:00:43,700
 tečajeve,

872
01:00:43,700 --> 01:00:44,480
 upravljanje novcem,

873
01:00:44,480 --> 01:00:44,960
 biblijskim.

874
01:00:44,960 --> 01:00:46,360
 Najviše mjesta u Bibliji

875
01:00:46,360 --> 01:00:47,380
 piše o materijalnom.

876
01:00:47,380 --> 01:00:49,440
 Upravljanju materijalnom.

877
01:00:49,440 --> 01:00:50,400
 Više nego o Isusu,

878
01:00:50,400 --> 01:00:51,200
 više o Mesiji,

879
01:00:51,200 --> 01:00:52,940
 više nego o zdravljanju,

880
01:00:52,940 --> 01:00:53,540
