881
01:00:53,540 --> 01:00:54,340
 Božjim prorocima,

882
01:00:54,340 --> 01:00:55,420
 najviše o materijalnom.

883
01:00:55,420 --> 01:00:56,440
 pa zna Bog

884
01:00:56,440 --> 01:00:58,200
 gdje smo najslabiji.

885
01:01:00,640 --> 01:01:01,960
 sve to mora ući

886
01:01:01,960 --> 01:01:03,220
 u naš program.

887
01:01:07,720 --> 01:01:09,280
 tako da ću završiti s tim.

888
01:01:09,280 --> 01:01:10,620
 Mercova ideja

889
01:01:10,620 --> 01:01:12,060
 Orlovstva je bila

890
01:01:12,060 --> 01:01:13,180
 i svrha Orla je bila

891
01:01:13,180 --> 01:01:13,440
 da

892
01:01:13,440 --> 01:01:15,200
 na svakom mjestu,

893
01:01:15,200 --> 01:01:16,180
 u svakom gradu

894
01:01:16,180 --> 01:01:18,280
 gdje se okupljaju mladi

895
01:01:18,280 --> 01:01:19,980
 organizira manifestacije,

896
01:01:19,980 --> 01:01:20,540
 događaje,

897
01:01:20,540 --> 01:01:21,340
 duhovne obrame,

898
01:01:21,340 --> 01:01:22,300
 duhovne vježbe

899
01:01:22,300 --> 01:01:24,320
 koje izgrađuju

900
01:01:24,320 --> 01:01:25,100
